# API Service

The API service is a Node.js backend located in [apps/api](mdc:apps/api).

## Key Files
- [apps/api/src/index.ts](mdc:apps/api/src/index.ts) - Main API entry point

## Configuration
- [apps/api/package.json](mdc:apps/api/package.json) - Dependencies and scripts
- [apps/api/tsconfig.json](mdc:apps/api/tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration

## Development
To run the API service in development mode:
```bash
pnpm dev:api
```
